Class DefaultSWRLRuleEngine

java.lang.Object
com.sebastienguillemin.wswrl.engine.DefaultSWRLRuleEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.swrlapi.core.SWRLRuleEngine
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultWSWRLRuleEngine
public class DefaultSWRLRuleEngine extends Object implements org.swrlapi.core.SWRLRuleEngine
This class provides an implementation of some of the core functionality required by a SWRL rule engine.
This implementation is taken from the SWRLAPI.
